<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">15</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>Most coughs go away on their own, but call your doctor if:</h2></div></div>
<div class="slide_text">
<ul class="rmq_answers">
<li class="user_answer">
<span class="answered_title"> </span>
<span class="you_answered_text">You answered: </span>
<span class="answer_text"> </span>
