<div class="answer_expl">
<div class="expl_content">
<p>Noisy breathing can be a symptom of bronchitis, asthma, or another problem that a doctor should check. Call them if you have trouble breathing or cough up blood. If your baby has a cough that worries you, call their doctor.</p>
