<div class="slide_media"> <div class="rmq_progress"><span class="cur_prog_title">Answer </span><span class="cur_prog_num">1</span>/<span class="tot_prog_num">15</span></div><div class="slide_question"><h2>A cough that brings up yellow-green mucus means you have a sinus infection.</h2></div></div>
